fields.name: dx
fields.description: X axis shift at the origin (accepted range is +/- 5000.0 meters).

fields.name: dy
fields.description: Y axis shift at the origin (accepted range is +/- 5000.0 meters).

fields.name: dz
fields.description: Z axis shift at the origin (accepted range is +/- 5000.0 meters).

fields.name: rotX
fields.description: Rotation about the X axis (accepted range is +/- 20.0 milli-arc seconds).

fields.name: rotY
fields.description: Rotation about the Y axis (accepted range is +/- 20.0 milli-arc seconds).

fields.name: rotZ
fields.description: Rotation about the Z axis (accepted range is +/- 20.0 milli-arc seconds).

fields.name: scale
fields.description: Scale change (accepted range is 0.0 to 50.0 parts per million).

issues: Extracted the 'POLL' variant (length 0) instead of the requested 'SET' variant (length 44).

adjudication.reasoning: The message UBX-CFG-DAT has the same ID (0x06-0x06) for Poll, Get, and Set operations. The 'Set' operation specifically requires a 44-byte payload. Eight out of nine extractions correctly identified the 44-byte structure. Extraction 1 incorrectly provided the POLL variant. Minor differences in casing for field names (majA vs maja) and units ('s' vs 'S' for seconds) exist between documentation versions but the data types, offsets, and logical structure are identical across all valid extractions.
